snippet.title: Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising - EVO Japan 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising is on the horizon, with an online beta test arriving in May!

This showcase of new battle mechanics from GBVS: Rising premiered at EVO Japan 2023, featuring a teaser for the next playable character, Siegfried.

Official Granblue Fantasy Versus Twitter
https://twitter.com/gbvs_official

Official Website - Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising (English)
https://rising.granbluefantasy.jp/en/

Official Website - Granblue Fantasy (Japanese)
https://granbluefantasy.jp/


#GBVS #GBVSR #GranblueFantasy #Cygames
